text: Daniela Oronova (born 6 April 1965) is a Bulgarian rower. She competed at the 1988 Summer Olympics, 1992 Summer Olympics and the 1996 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1965 births Category:Living people Category:Bulgarian female rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Bulgaria Category:Rowers at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Rowers at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Rowers from Sofia
